{
  "id": "RAW_c9a46b51",
  "title": "按场景来服务「人」，腾讯会议的 AI 情商好高",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU2Njg0OTEyNQ==&mid=2247490603&idx=1&sn=d5bec2c86d94b2942f3be80fb86d1a9f",
  "date": "2026-01-01 02:01:00",
  "author": "AI异类弗兰克",
  "siteName": "AI异类弗兰克",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 3 []\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">最近一段时间，我对“会议”这件事的耐心在明显下降。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">不是不想认真，</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">是开会多了就</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">发现，今天的大多数会议，</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">更多不是在解决问题</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">，</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">是因为程序正义和人情世故。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">开会，成了</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一个</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">对我来说有点</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">信息过载、注意力分散、情绪与态度被不断稀释</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">的问题。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">远程会议尤其明显，摄像头关掉，语气变平，表态模糊，真正重要的判断</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">和结论不一定有，还经常</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">藏在一句看似随口的话里，或者一次短暂的沉默中。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所以我对会议类 AI 产品的期待，其实早就从帮我记下来，变成了——</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">能不能帮我判断，这场会真正发生了什么</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">就像更聪明的职场人，能听懂弦外之音，不是像个小实习生一样只会埋头一字不落记笔记。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">也是在这种心态下，我重新认真用了一段时间腾讯会议的「AI纪要」，以及它最近上线的多模板功能。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">坦白说，这次更新给我的感觉不是功能又多了，是</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">产品终于开始按场景来思考人</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">了。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.683991683991684\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"962\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"395\" data-imgfileid=\"100006707\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d94468d0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F9CRQL8peAG0cj9BMArC7LwsLP7JEXy6ULLcDbsat0wJTfTs6IZicAYeDCnABTY1iadwXJw3DozWBbl5iaBNmdg5Kw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">从「会议助手」到多模板，重构AI对会议的理解方式</span></span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">如果你之前用过腾讯会议 AI纪要，对它的基础能力大概率已经不陌生。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">理解会议内容同时听懂言外之意</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">、自动总结、每两分钟推送一次阶段性纪要，这些都已经是相对成熟、稳定、可靠的能力了。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">真正让我对这次更新重新提起兴趣的，是一个变化方向：</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">AI纪要不再假设“所有人开会的目的都一样”</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.49166666666666664\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" height=\"272.611\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;width: 554.133px;height: 272.611px;\" width=\"554.133\" data-imgfileid=\"100006675\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=38acb9fa&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F9CRQL8peAG0dyYqVFJayFhRI0EehkWAueNKNYBQDT26e2jQL6JbYdibTYVv9ZzlsXen5gBJv8law5LaSRGwIyZw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">以前只有一个「会议助手」模板，本质上是“通用会议理解”。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">现在开始分化出「学霸笔记」「面试助手」，再叠加原本的会议场景，其实是在做一件很关键的事情</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">：</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">把同一套底层 AI 能力，调成不同“心智模式”</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这是很多 AI 产品容易忽略的一点。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">模型可能已经很强了，但怎么用，往往决定了</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">9</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">0%的体验差异。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">回过头来看，其实无论是对会议语气的判断，还是</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">实时</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">推送的纪要，本身都不是某一个新模板才突然出现的能力，而是从最早的「会议助手」阶段，AI 纪要就已经在尝试做的事情。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一方面，通过按人查看观点、风险提示、待办事项等更清晰的结构拆分，那些原本藏在话语里的迟疑、保留和潜在阻力，被更准确地放进了对应的语境里；</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">另一方面，每</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">2</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">分钟一次的阶段性纪要，也不再只是简单的过程回顾，而是不断帮你把注意力重新拉回到当前讨论的核心判断上。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这些能力本身并不新，但在新的功能形态下，你会更明显地意识到：</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">AI 纪要关注的，已经不只是“记下了什么”，而是“这场会议此刻真正发生了什么”。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">也正是从这里开始，我第一次感觉到，它开始更接近人类在真实会议中的理解方式，而不是单纯做一个记录工具。</span></span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">真正拉开差距的，是「学霸笔记」这个模板</span></span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">如果说前面的能力更多是面向职场会议，那么「学霸笔记」这个模板，是我觉得这次更新里</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">最干净、最明确的一次场景落地</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">打开腾讯会议，切换到 AI纪要里的「学霸笔记」，你会明显感受到，它对信息的取舍逻辑变了。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6121979286536249\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1738\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100006688\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e6fef445&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F9CRQL8peAG0cj9BMArC7LwsLP7JEXy6UibibrqIlSMAeXIwvUG9ydFkvjJmkDyiazy6Sc7ibH7jOZJcF3QfxF2w1mw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我发现它没那么</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">强调“谁说了什么”，</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">看清了</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">更接近课堂笔记的结构：</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">重点自动加粗，概念和定义被明确区分，难点会被单独标注，整体呈现出一种非常“学习友好”的层次感。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我试着用它记录了一场线上课程，最大的感受是——</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">你不需要一边听一边担心“这句话要不要记”</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">AI已经在替你做第一轮筛选和结构整理，你更多是在理解，</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">不用</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">抄写</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">不用在意咬文嚼字的细节</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">更有意思的是，学霸笔记可以一键导入腾讯元宝。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" height=\"369.42225721784774\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;width: 554.133px;height: 369.422px;\" width=\"554.1333333333333\" data-imgfileid=\"100006672\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b4f9c073&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F9CRQL8peAG0dyYqVFJayFhRI0EehkWAuUf3GWeHofWoB6fuwzrSRibYRHBCYtxDpgicXE1rkqr84BCqP8VOWD6iaA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">把整堂课的内容丢给元宝之后，你可以直接让它生成思维导图、重点总结，甚至是随堂测验题。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这一步，其实完成了从“记录”到“消化”的闭环。对学生、备考党、甚至终身学习者来说，这是一个非常实用、而且真实可用的组合。</span></span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"display: inline-block;overflow: hidden;transform: rotate(0deg);width: 554.133px;height: 369.422px;text-indent: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1920\" height=\"369.422\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;width: 554.133px;height: 369.422px;\" width=\"554.133\" data-imgfileid=\"100006694\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d3451e31&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F9CRQL8peAG0cj9BMArC7LwsLP7JEXy6USicgjnGaxOuYTEz9ygJChoHmzGHk1kMzrDBS7L9PCrse9pVnYfXxGdQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></span></h2>\n  <h2 style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">面试助手，是一个</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">「</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">很懂人紧张</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">」</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">的 AI</span></span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">相比学霸笔记的清晰直接，「面试助手」给我的感觉是——</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">它对人的状态理解得更细</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">开启面试助手后，你几乎不需要额外操作，系统会自动识别你是面试官还是面试者，然后给出完全不同的支持方式。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">站在面试官视角，它不仅帮你记录候选人的关键信息，还会在过程中提示一些“值得追问的点”。这种提示不是打断式的，而是类似一个在旁边低声提醒你的同事，让你意识到：“这个地方，可能值得再问一句。”</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">更重要的是，会后你可以把这份 AI纪要直接丢给元宝，让它基于整场面试内容，构建一个候选人评估视图。从技能、表达、逻辑、应变等多个维度进行总结，这在集中招聘场景下，真的能显著降低遗漏和主观偏差。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而站在面试者视角，面试助手反而显得更“温和”。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5116959064327485\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2736\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"296\" data-imgfileid=\"100006710\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b45ce132&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F9CRQL8peAG0cj9BMArC7LwsLP7JEXy6UiaRA4No08mjCP72xsYFK9KwCr6dHkqicT3T3Zj51uTWXAbLo5H5eXo1g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">它会在你表达得比较好的时候给予即时反馈，让你清楚地知道：</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">哪一段回答是加分项</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">。同时，当你开始陷入细节、逻辑变散时，它也会给出非常克制的提醒，帮助你重新拉回结构。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">最让我印象深刻的，是它对“问题潜台词”的解读。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">有些面试问题表面很开放，但真正考察的点非常具体。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">面试助手会提示你，对方可能更关注预算、转化率或落地经验，从而帮你更精准地回应。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">都不只是</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">替</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">人</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">回答</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">了</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">，而是在帮</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">人</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">听懂</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">背后的小九九</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">。</span></span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">分人查看观点，让会议第一次“按人还原”</span></span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">AI纪要最近上线的「分人查看观点」功能，其实非常符合我对会议理解的一种偏执。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">会议由人组成，事情也是由人推动的。把所有发言混在一起总结，往往会抹平责任和立场。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">分人查看观点这个视角，相当于把信息流重新拆解，让你清楚看到：谁在推动，谁在犹豫，谁在反对。对管理者来说，这是理解团队状态的一个非常直观的方式。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">配合历史会议自动沉淀、图片分享等功能，AI纪要正在变成一种“会议资产”的管理工具，而不只是一次性的记录。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.49166666666666664\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" height=\"272.6109186351706\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;width: 554.133px;height: 272.611px;\" width=\"554.1333333333333\" data-imgfileid=\"100006678\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c596a04a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F9CRQL8peAG0dyYqVFJayFhRI0EehkWAukaLOW65vBPdfH2NxzTqBibsjwJaT54YENWiaXx9ctxdT1B6YdN3EzffQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">一点更大的感受：AI，终于开始为具体的人服务了</span></span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">写到这里，我其实更想说的是一个更宏观的判断。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">AI 的竞争，早就不只是模型参数和榜单了。真正决定体验的，是它能不能在具体场景里，理解人的真实需求。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">腾讯会议 AI纪要这次的多模板进化，</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我觉得得</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">承认一件事：</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">同样是说话、听话、记录，不同场景下的“好用”，标准是完全不一样的</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6111111111111112\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" height=\"338.8330708661417\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;width: 554.133px;height: 338.833px;\" width=\"554.1333333333333\" data-imgfileid=\"100006679\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=335c9004&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F9CRQL8peAG0dyYqVFJayFhRI0EehkWAu44ARhvic9bWnZHlZYasjLnwmzRtlIA5t0SZl6rJ5uuoLD0tlNAn5pYw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">会议、课堂、面试，每一个场景都有不同的紧张点、判断逻辑和价值目标。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">AI能不能调对姿态</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">、应对得当</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">，比它会不会总结更重要。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而通过与腾讯元宝的打通，这些能力不再停留在记录完就结束，</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">那还是死笔记。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">可以被追问、被扩展、被真正用于决策和学习</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">，纪要才算活过来。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">如果说过去的 AI 会议工具，是在帮你少干点活，那现在的方向，更像是在帮你</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">少错过</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">、更精明</span></span></span><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 3pt 16px;\"><span style=\"\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这可能才是 AI 真正走向日常、走向长期价值的方式。</span></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文深度评测了腾讯会议 AI 纪要的多模板更新，分析其如何通过场景化心智模式，实现从单纯记录到深度理解会议潜台词的转变。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文深度评测了腾讯会议 AI 纪要的多模板更新，分析其如何通过场景化心智模式，实现从单纯记录到深度理解会议潜台词的转变。",
  "summary": "文章探讨了腾讯会议 AI 纪要功能的最新演进，核心观点认为 AI 产品已从“通用总结”转向“场景化服务”。通过引入「学霸笔记」、「面试助手」等特定模板，AI 能够根据不同场景调整其信息过滤和逻辑处理方式。例如，「学霸笔记」侧重知识点的结构化提取与元宝生态的联动；「面试助手」则侧重于识别面试官与候选人的不同需求，甚至能解读问题的“潜台词”。此外，功能如“分人查看观点”进一步强化了对会议中人际博弈和立场推动的还原，标志着 AI 会议工具正从提效工具向决策辅助和资产管理工具进化。",
